Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Building 1, Equinox Business Park is located in the heart of Deakin which offers a mix of commercial and medical suites to occupiers.  Within proximity to the Parliamentary Triangle, Woden Town Centre and Canberra CBD, this is a prime location for a range of businesses.

The landmark Business Parks consists of three primary A grade buildings which allow a wide permitted use including office and medical.  Each has excellent natural light, efficient floor plates, lift access and services to meet an A grade standard.  Basement parking and on-site parking is available for occupiers and staff within the Business Park.  End of trip facilities are available for Staff as well as on site café EQ, Bakehouse and The Den Canberra.

Available for lease in Building 1:

Part Ground Floor: 235sqm* Open plan ready for fitout suitable for medical

Part level 2: 282sqm* Refurbished open plan space ready for fit out – good frontage onto central glass corridor. May be subdivided to two suites of 125sqm and 155sqm.

Level 3: 812sqm* Refurbished open plan space ready for fit out which includes a 122sqm* terrace


For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Deakin.One is a new kind of workplace: One that nurtures its inhabitants and fosters – through its balance of design and amenity – a higher level of productivity and satisfaction.

Centrally located, Deakin.One is connected, close to major arterial routes linking it with the Canberra City CBD, Parliamentary Triangle and Canberra Airport.

With its outlook over serene green spaces and its high level of amenity, Deakin.One is the prefect location to combine work and wellness to promote collaborative thinking and to attract and retain the best talent in your industry.

This exciting new development features 8,000sqm of state of the art office accommodation over 3 levels connected by a central atrium allowing natural light to diffuse through the space. 

Key Highlights:

•	2 Levels of secure basement parking
•	Designed to achieve a 4.5- Star NABERS Rating
•	Market leading EOT facilities
•	Efficient floor plates
•	Proposed onsite café
•	Surrounded by amenity and green spaces
•	Suitable for office or medical

For further information please visit the website www.deakinone.com.au or contact the exclusive marketing agents.
